{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Emits the [ListModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/listmodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on "},{"code":"list","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","externalID":"s:3GIO17ListModelProtocolPAAE12itemsChanged8position7removed5addedySi_S2itF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO9ListStoreC","roleHeading":"Instance Method","extendedModule":"GIO","role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore\/ListModelProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/liststore\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"position","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"removed"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"added"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This function should only be called by classes implementing","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". It has to be called after the internal representation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"list"},{"text":" has been updated, because handlers connected to this signal","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"might query the new state of the list.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementations must only make changes to the model (as visible to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"its consumer) in places that will not cause problems for that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"consumer.  For models that are driven directly by a write API (such"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"), changes can be reported in response to uses of that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"API.  For models that represent remote data, changes should only be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"made from a fresh mainloop dispatch.  It is particularly not","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"permitted to make changes in response to a call to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumer API.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Stated another way: in general, it is assumed that code making a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"series of accesses to the model via the API, without returning to the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"mainloop, and without calling other code, will continue to view the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"same contents of the model."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ListStore":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ListStore"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore","title":"ListStore","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/liststore","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ListStore"}],"abstract":[{"code":"GListStore","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is a simple implementation of [iface","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":"] that stores","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all items in memory."}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ListStore/ListModelProtocol-Implementations":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore\/ListModelProtocol-Implementations","abstract":[],"role":"collectionGroup","title":"ListModelProtocol Implementations","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/liststore\/listmodelprotocol-implementations","kind":"article","type":"topic"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ListStore/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"itemsChanged","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"position"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"removed","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"added","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListStore\/itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","title":"itemsChanged(position:removed:added:)","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/liststore\/itemschanged(position:removed:added:)","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Emits the [ListModel](\/\/documentation\/gio\/listmodel\/onitemschanged(flags:handler:) signal on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"list"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/ListModel":{"title":"ListModel","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/listmodel","abstract":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GListModel"},{"text":" is an interface that represents a mutable list of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[class[Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object]. Its main intention is as a model for various widgets"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in user interfaces, such as list views, but it can also be used as a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"convenient method of returning lists of data, with support for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"updates.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ListModel","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ListModel","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"ListModel"}]}}}